{"tid":2270868,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鮑彤轟五中全會一言堂 背離法治","createTime":"2020-11-04T08:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T09:04:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e03f170a93872c6a76dd1d40796bc308302299e0","tid":2270868,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201104/4J7I3H4ZGZGOLNWWA372HWOER4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201104%2F4J7I3H4ZGZGOLNWWA372HWOER4%2F&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcysmKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=0d3935bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201104%2F4J7I3H4ZGZGOLNWWA372HWOER4%2F&h=30dc7c2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201104/4J7I3H4ZGZGOLNWWA372HWOER4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鮑彤轟五中全會一言堂 背離法治<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/4Qk7oS7cFuhOyRuavng1BIH0rD4=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KNY22EPYJBGL3MNBJS63MSN4F4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F4Qk7oS7cFuhOyRuavng1BIH0rD4%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKNY22EPYJBGL3MNBJS63MSN4F4.jpg&h=aa4f2888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中共前總書記趙紫陽政治秘書鮑彤（圖）<br />\n<br />\n前日在自由亞洲電台投稿，評論五中全會。他認為，中共十九屆五中全會搞一言堂，開闢「核心一言定乾坤」的新時代，而且背離法治，宣示2035年前，不可能實施「法律面前人人平等」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：十四五《建議》公佈 稱落實全面治權  政治先行 港恐「越管越死」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指習近平核心體制「永續」<br />\n<br />\n鮑彤指，五中全會前月，發生了一件不尋常的事：9月28日，中共中央政治局制定《中國共產黨中央委員會工作條例》；兩天後，中央政治局發佈這條例，宣佈立即生效。五中全會必須照此開會，不得有誤。他又指，不得有誤的精華，簡稱「兩個維護」，就是「中共中央委員會必須帶頭做到」堅決維護習近平黨中央的核心、全黨的核心地位，及堅決維護黨中央權威和統一領導。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n鮑彤又直指五中全會背離法治路線。他進一步解釋，2015年12月，中。。。。。。。。。，做不到「法律面前人人平等」。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台"},{"pid":"4ff7f53b461d91d66a29d3622b61e637d3774004","tid":2270868,"uid":375068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:03:40.000Z","msg":"法治？"},{"pid":"6b433c99571bf3a36c87dd210c4a977a5a9667ad","tid":2270868,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T09:04:48.000Z","msg":"唔講以為之前有法治過囉"}]}